    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-host004.m4a",
      "text": "熱戦の末、ここに新たなBIG4が誕生しました！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After a heated battle‚ a new BIG4 has been born!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0559368623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私達が、勝った……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won‚‚‚?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0191571407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0191571407
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1574567648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "スコアを見る限り、そうみたい……ですけど\n見間違いじゃ……ありませんよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems that way‚ judging by the score‚‚‚ but\nI can't believe it's‚‚‚ real‚‚‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0666655633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.6477966797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだよ、琴乃ちゃん、沙季ちゃん……！\n私達、どりきゅんに勝ったんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it's real‚ Kotono‚ Saki!\nWe beat DoriKyun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6999988966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.3156425647
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.8489820015
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "やりましたわ！　私達の大勝利ですわよー！！\nご覧なさい芽衣、この結果を……うぅ……うわぁぁん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We did it! This is our great victory~!\nSee this‚ Mei? This is the result‚‚‚ sniffle‚‚‚ Waaaah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8489820015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、やったね！\n頑張ったもんね、すずにゃんも、みんなも、すっごく！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ you did it!\nYou worked hard‚ Suzu-nyan‚ everyone‚ really hard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1999988966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.9519467842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "……負けたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‚‚‚We lost‚ huh‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9519467842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-lmn001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。僅差だけど、負けは負け",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ It was close‚ but a loss is a loss‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7849855117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.8290220591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれだけ煽っといて負けてたら、世話ねぇな\nおい、琴乃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's embarrassing to lose after talking big like that‚\nHey‚ Kotono‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9333322299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.703761388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "来夢さん、れもんさん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lime-san‚ Lemon-san‚‚‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.703761388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 96.9328988966
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.9329225711
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-lim003.m4a",
      "text": "あたしらは真剣勝負をした。全力を尽くした\nそして、負けた。……けじめはつけさせてもらう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We fought a serious match‚ We gave it our all‚\nAnd we lost‚ ‚‚‚We'll take responsibility‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2333322299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.0946225017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "あなた達の望みは何かしら\nやっぱり、私達の解散？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it you want?\nOur disbandment‚ I presume?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9666655633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0282202252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、解散なんて求めません。そんなことじゃなくて\nお二人には、絶対に解散しないでほしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we don't want you to disband‚ That's not what we want‚\nWe want you two to never disband‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0666655633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "それが、私の望みです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is my wish‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.420421331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.420421331
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7258871882
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 127.4333322299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-lim004.m4a",
      "text": "……あ？\n恥を晒して生きろってのか？　お前らみたいに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‚‚‚Huh?\nYou want us to live in shame? Like you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3666655633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.8642583378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……お二人は、いつか言ってましたよね。「この世界を\n変革して、アイドルを世界一のエンタメにする」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‚‚‚You two said it before‚ \"We're going to\nrevolutionize this world‚ and make idols the greatest entertainment in the world‚\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4333322299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
