      "text": "私は、自分より弱い者をこの世界から追い出すような\nお二人のやり方に賛成は出来ません。今も、これからも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't agree with your methods of driving out those weaker than yourselves from this world‚\nNot now‚ not ever‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.9999988966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.3699730723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
