      "text": "でもお二人の想いは……\nそれだけは、否定しちゃいけないと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But your feelings‚‚‚\nI believe that's something we shouldn't deny‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8666655633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.3583360203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
