      "text": "今ここで辞めたら、その想いはどこに行くんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you quit here and now‚ where will those feelings go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3583360203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
